wiki.text:
'Domicile' may refer to:

* In architecture, a general term for a place of residence<!--leave link to
  article dab since "residence" can mean multiple kinds of builings/places where
  one resides--> or "permanent residence" in legal terms
* Domicile (astrology), the zodiac sign over which a planet has rulership
* Domicile (law), the status or attribution of being a permanent resident in a
  particular jurisdiction
* Domicile (airline), a location where aircrew are centered to staff aircraft.
  These locations are typically at a scheduled service passenger airline's,
  cargo airline's, or charter airline's main focus city or hub in larger
  metropolitan areas.
* In product packaging, the manufacturer information, sometimes located near the
  UPC or on the side of the package <!--* Domicile, a thrash metal band from
  Manchester, England-->
